# `math sinh` for [math](/commands/categories/math.md)

<div class='command-title'>Returns the hyperbolic sine of the number.</div>

## Signature

```> math sinh {flags} ```


## Input/output types:

| input        | output      |
| ------------ | ----------- |
| number       | float       |
| list&lt;number&gt; | list&lt;float&gt; |
## Examples

Apply the hyperbolic sine to 1
```nu
> 1 | math sinh

```
